### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Execute Command - Simple command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "pwd"
}

### Execute Command - List files
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "ls -la"
}

### Execute Command - Check current user
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "whoami"
}

### Execute Command - Long running command (for testing cancellation)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "sleep 30 && echo 'Done sleeping'"
}

### Cancel Command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "job_id": "290631e1-247b-4ed2-9464-b1d9ad5048e8"
}

### Execute Command - System info
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "uname -a"
}

### Execute Command - Check disk space
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "df -h"
}